<dl>
<dd><i>This article describes only the common terms, rules, and procedures of betting in poker. See <a href="/wiki/Poker_strategy" title="Poker strategy">poker strategy</a> for the strategic impact of betting.</i></dd>
</dl>
<p>In the game of <a href="/wiki/Poker" title="Poker">poker</a>, the play largely centers around the act of <a href="/wiki/Gambling" title="Gambling">betting</a>, and as such, a protocol has been developed to speed play, lessen confusion, and increase security while playing. Different games are played using different types of bets, and small variations in etiquette exist between <a href="/wiki/Cardroom" title="Cardroom">cardrooms</a>, but for the most part the following rules and protocol are observed by the majority of poker players.</p>
