</tr>
<tr>
<td>$20 from first round</td>
<td>$20 Starting Pot</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Player A bets $5</td>
<td>$20 Starting Pot
<p>$&#160;&#160;5 Player A's Bet<br />
â€”â€”â€”<br />
